<p><b>People</b>
</p>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Don_A._Allen#Positions" title="Don A. Allen">Don A. Allen</a>, member of the California State Assembly and of the Los Angeles City Council in the 1940s and 1950s, urged enforcement of curfew laws.</li></ul>
